y bishop of Myra in Lycia, about whom virtually nothing factual is known, although a vast body of legend grew up around him, and he became the patron saint of Greece and of Russia, as well as of children, sailors, merchants, and pawnbrokers. His feast day is  6 December , and among the many roles which legend has assigned to him is that of bringer of Christmas presents, in the guise of ‘Santa Claus’ (an alteration of the Dutch form of his name, <i>Sinterklaas</i>)."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"When Niels Thorkilsen Bugge was born about 1240, in Glenstrup, Hobro, Nordjylland, Denmark, his father, Turild Bugge, was 27 and his mother, Mrs. Bugge, was 27. He had at least 1 son with Andersdatter. He died about 1310, in Lyby, Lyby, Nørre, Viborg, Denmark, at the age of 72."},"et":{"About 1240–About 1310":"umbes 1240–umbes 1310","1240–1310":"1240–1310","1240–Male":"1240–Surnud","1245–Female":"1245–Surnud","1270–1332":"1270–1332","1215–1302":"1215–1302","1215–1270":"1215–1270","About 1270":"umbes 1270","1215":"1215","about 1270":"umbes 1270","1302":"1302","1245":"1245","1332":"1332","1310":"1310","Abt 1302":"umbes 1302","1240":"1240","About 1310":"umbes 1310","1270":"1270","About 1240":"umbes 1240","Hegnet, Tøndering, Harre, Viborg, Danmark":"Hegnet, Tøndering, Harre, Viborg, Taani","Glenstrup, Hobro, Randers, Denmark":"Glenstrup, Nørhald, Randers, Taani","Lyby, Lyby, Nørre, Viborg, Danmark":"Lyby, Lyby, Nørre, Viborg, Taani","Glenstrup Bakker, Hobro, Danmark":"Glenstrup, Hobro, Nordjylland, Taani"},"fi":{"About 1240–About 1310":"noin 1240–noin 1310","1240–1310":"1240–1310","1240–Male":"1240–Kuollut","1245–Female":"1245–Kuollut","1270–1332":"1270–1332","1215–1302":"1215–1302","1215–1270":"1215–1270","About 1270":"noin 1270","1215":"1215","about 1270":"noin 1270","1302":"1302","1245":"1245","1332":"1332","1310":"1310","Abt 1302":"noin 1302","1240":"1240","About 1310":"noin 1310","1270":"1270","About 1240":"noin 1240","Hegnet, Tøndering, Harre, Viborg, Danmark":"Hegnet, Tøndering, Ha